We do a lot
more than fly
Western

We provide Group Specialists
By making special arrangements for meetings,
incentive programs, conventions and charters, we
give you and your group VIP attention.
We also have low fares for groups as small as ten.
We give you easy credit
You can apply for a Western Charge-a-Flight card
and fly to any place in Western's Worid. Western
also accepts most major credit cards.
We pamper your baggage
No matter where you sit on the plane, your
baggage always rides "first class.' On most flights,
we even place it in a special container marked for
your destination... sealed and protected.
We cater to your cargo
Nearly every Western flight features special
containerized baggage protection for all of your
Air Cargo, so it always gets "First Class handling"
We have special programs, too, such as our new
SPEED PAK SERVICE Instant Cargo. And,
remember, all Western flights are Air Cargo flights.
